Policy.acknowledgement_statement: The dataset used for the analysis in this manuscript were obtained from dbGaP through accession study number (phs00xxxx), and was funded in part by the support from Merck & Co. Additional information regarding the study population and genomic research can be found in Hao et al. PLoS Genet 8.11 (2012): e1003029. We would like to thank the participants in this study and the research groups at Laval University, University of British Columbia, and University of Groningen for their valuable contribution to this research.
Policy.ic_specific_access_term: Use of the data must be related to Lung Disease. Requestor must provide documentation of local IRB approval. Requestor must provide a letter of collaboration with the primary study investigator(s). Use of the data is limited to not-for-profit organizations. Use of the data is limited to genetic studies only.
